1. install truffle
npm install -g truffle
https://truffleframework.com/docs/truffle/getting-started/installation

2. install ganache (in mem ethereum)
https://truffleframework.com/ganache

3. install metamask, connect metamask to ganache,
import some accounts from ganache.
https://metamask.io/

4. install lite-server
npm install lite-server --save-dev

3. run 
npm run dev
